import { Box, Card, CardContent, CardMedia, Typography } from "@mui/material";



export const Product = () => {

    return (
        <>
            <Box sx={{ gap: "20px", display: "flex", width: "100vw", justifyContent: "space-around", marginTop: "100px" }}>

                <Card sx={{ maxWidth: 345 }}>
                    <CardMedia
                        component="img"
                        height="140"
                        image="https://dummyjson.com/image/i/products/1/1.jpg"
                        alt="green iguana"
                    />
                    <CardContent>
                        <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                            Iphone-9
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                            NUMBERS RAKHNI HOOO
                        </Typography>
                    </CardContent>
                </Card>

                <Card sx={{ maxWidth: 345 }}>
                <CardMedia
                        component="img"
                        height="140"
                        image="https://dummyjson.com/image/i/products/11/thumbnail.jpg"
                    />
                    <CardContent>
                        <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                           Perfume
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                            NUMBERS RAKHNI HOOO
                        </Typography>
                    </CardContent>
                </Card>

                <Card sx={{ maxWidth: 345 }}>
                <CardMedia
                        component="img"
                        height="140"
                        image="https://dummyjson.com/image/i/products/18/thumbnail.jpg"
                    />
                    <CardContent>
                        <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                            Bag
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                            NUMBERS RAKHNI HOOO
                        </Typography>
                    </CardContent>
                </Card>

                <Card sx={{ maxWidth: 345 }}>
                    <CardContent>
                        <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                            Earing
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                            NUMBERS RAKHNI HOOO
                        </Typography>
                    </CardContent>
                </Card>
            </Box>

        </>


    )
};
